{"tid":113022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼影院雙人床位惹議 女副市長怒：促進通姦","createTime":"2017-02-08T15:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T04:26:14.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1874802171707c68b272a423bf22a480a8e5b6d","tid":113022,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"2017-02-08  17:36<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕印尼一豪華電影院，為提供觀眾更舒適的觀影空間，設置了豪華雙人床位，但巨港（Palembang）女副市長對此相當憤怒，認為這會促進通姦，要求改善否則吊銷執照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/feb/8/images/bigPic/400_400/phpuiXr6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Ffeb%2F8%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2FphpuiXr6Y.jpg&h=36d26066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印尼巨港市一豪華電影院，為提供觀眾更舒適的觀影空間，設置了豪華雙人床位。（圖取自Cinta Fitri臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，印尼連鎖影城CGV設置了豪華的天鵝絨雙人床，配有枕頭、毯子等，該設施已在雅加達、印尼多地運行多年並無發生問題，但近日卻引發民眾投訴，巨港女副市長Fitrianti Agustinda為此在日前前往影城進行視察，她對豪華床位相當不滿，認為這可能促進通姦。<br />\nFitrianti Agustinda表示，她要一個解釋，「這種設計，如果人們不想看電影，他們還可以用這床做點別的事！」CGV的經理則試圖緩頰沒必要這麼擔心，雙人床位不僅適用夫妻，還可讓一般家庭更舒適地看電影。<br />\n但Fitrianti Agustinda對解釋並不買帳，下令關閉電影院，直到業主把床位改成一般座位，若影城不遵守命令，營業執照將被吊銷。CGV最後也同意進行必要修改。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/feb/8/images/bigPic/400_400/php1KGuc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Ffeb%2F8%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2Fphp1KGuc9.jpg&h=881051ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巨港女副市長Fitrianti Agustinda在日前前往影城進行視察，她對豪華床位相當不滿，認為這可能促進通姦。（圖取自Cinta Fitri臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1968599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1968599&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c2d56f29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1968599&h=184fc491\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1968599</a>"},{"pid":"be61917825d08b35c7a0f9daebcc1c4f184b124e","tid":113022,"uid":41638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"女人講野都無腦"},{"pid":"6a9ebe11e2451dee383dc09db3fe16065d64a160","tid":113022,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:13:35.000Z","msg":"屌 咁多人當眾扑野咩<br />\n要通姦就爆房啦"},{"pid":"f0b5bee8e65130ae701352b3c26eb66ba9b97bb6","tid":113022,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:22:28.000Z","msg":"佢係咪未結婚"},{"pid":"d74f4954a50d8d5e30603b0f68b8d02021fec496","tid":113022,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:28:22.000Z","msg":"又係d無腦蛔民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7711bf2eb3b3d501848e0d7fdb67c2606547034a","tid":113022,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:48:55.000Z","msg":"香港有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32290d497759d3390e5aa3aaae70ada250b69322","tid":113022,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:50:17.000Z","msg":"執柒晒啲酒店佢囉"},{"pid":"a957786a5321ca25dc0eca44391f22b0a919700e","tid":113022,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:52:08.000Z","msg":"出面扮矜持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係屋就至撚淫賤"},{"pid":"361f6205252da9c4986d9c952a19b33017ed2ac5","tid":113022,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:54:42.000Z","msg":"d老處女真係惡撚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911ef84e4f0017a3db4507c220e3889342f5a62d","tid":113022,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:07:36.000Z","msg":"女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a4f6bdd5dadbb18a09f763ffdceba1cb81cb2d","tid":113022,"uid":22283,"like":0,"